    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rabbit was born and raised in Carrot’s Village, a small, sunny town surrounded by forest, where habitants lived in harmony. Small town, great rabbits!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A threat grew each day, as a dark entity lurked closer and closer to Carrot’s Village. The Steam Order discovered the power of steam machines, propelling them to power and conquest. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763860/extras/64f3f72339c87f9a61725fcf7b48bd7d.poster.avif?t=1759850095\" width=600 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763860/extras/64f3f72339c87f9a61725fcf7b48bd7d.webm?t=1759850095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763860/extras/64f3f72339c87f9a61725fcf7b48bd7d.mp4?t=1759850095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They threatened and took by force all the land they could, expanding their dominion thanks to their terrifying steam machines and cold-hearted minions. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One afternoon, they arrived at Carrot’s Village. A warning they gave, but a short one.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763860/extras/9da787040de3b1eaa32bdbf37f02b368.poster.avif?t=1759850095\" width=600 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763860/extras/9da787040de3b1eaa32bdbf37f02b368.webm?t=1759850095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763860/extras/9da787040de3b1eaa32bdbf37f02b368.mp4?t=1759850095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >By dawn everything was sacked, burning and destroyed. Families were torn apart by kidnappers with no soul. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now, our Hero finds himself alone with a mission on his hands. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763860/extras/c1c9f67c9c409cc753d7691578399cd8.poster.avif?t=1759850095\" width=600 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763860/extras/c1c9f67c9c409cc753d7691578399cd8.webm?t=1759850095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763860/extras/c1c9f67c9c409cc753d7691578399cd8.mp4?t=1759850095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game Features</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Metroidvania game: classic sidescrolling platform gameplay with an explorable, interconnected world. </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Engage in skilled fights and immersive action. </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Evolve new and powerful combat skills to fight your way through enemy waves and save Rabbit's family. </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Experience a Metroidvania mixed with Roguelike in a new way. </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Beautiful and intriguing landscapes. </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Mesmerizing soundtrack. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763860/extras/9ac282d193bd76a95a12dbdf4fdaaec3.poster.avif?t=1759850095\" width=600 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763860/extras/9ac282d193bd76a95a12dbdf4fdaaec3.webm?t=1759850095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763860/extras/9ac282d193bd76a95a12dbdf4fdaaec3.mp4?t=1759850095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763860/extras/b67b01878e7de7ae297351bef2655b6d.poster.avif?t=1759850095\" width=600 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763860/extras/b67b01878e7de7ae297351bef2655b6d.webm?t=1759850095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763860/extras/b67b01878e7de7ae297351bef2655b6d.mp4?t=1759850095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
